					<header>
						<h2>The Ultimate API</h2>
						<p>Get your plugin out there quicker, faster, and efficiently!</p>
						<p>Start, or add your plugin to the Ultimate API via your main class, and gain instant access to debuggers, loggers, and many other utilities commonly needed by plugin developers.</p>
					</header>
					<div class="row">
						<section class="feature 6u 12u$(small)">
							<h3 class="title">Packed With the Dispatcher</h3>
							<p>The Dispatcher allows you to dispatch information to the console quickly, and clearly with options to disable certain channels at runtime. (verbose on / off, etc.)</p>
						</section>
						<section class="feature 6u$ 12u$(small)">
							<h3 class="title">Modularity</h3>
							<p>Access other useful components, such as the Gui Class packed into one Class, or the Minigame Class for example.</p>
						</section>
